Company Overview of Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - Global Equity Portfolio



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - Global Equity Portfolio is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Harding Loevner LP. It invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as volatility and companies that are well managed, financially sound, fast growing, and strongly competitive to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio ag...
Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - Global Equity Portfolio is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Harding Loevner LP. It invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as volatility and companies that are well managed, financially sound, fast growing, and strongly competitive to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI All Country World (net) Index. The fund conducts proprietary research to make its investments. Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - Global Equity Portfolio was formed on December 1, 1996 and is domiciled in the United States.
