Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - International Equity Portfolio: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 1:15 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - International Equity Portfolio



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - International Equity Portfolio is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Harding Loevner LP. It invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe, excluding the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the growth and value stocks of companies across all capitalizations. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with bottom up stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as volatility and companies that are well managed, financially sound, fast growing, and strongly competitive to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the...
Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - International Equity Portfolio is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Harding Loevner LP. It invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe, excluding the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the growth and value stocks of companies across all capitalizations. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with bottom up stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as volatility and companies that are well managed, financially sound, fast growing, and strongly competitive to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI All Country World ex-U.S. (net) Index. The fund conducts proprietary research to make its investments. Harding, Loevner Funds, Inc. - International Equity Portfolio was formed on December 31, 1989 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


